snippet.title: Earthworm Jim 2 Trailer 1995
snippet.description:
Earthworm Jim 2 Trailer 1995

Official Content From Playmates Interactive

Earthworm Jim is back, and this time he's brought his friend Snott with him. New levels, moves and power-ups along with the slimy and not-so-slimy humor add to the fun.
Platforms: Sega Genesis, Super Nintendo
